file: BeforeToolCallResult.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Tool\\BeforeToolCallResult"
type: readonly final class
summary: Represents the outcome of a pre-execution validation check for a tool call within the agent domain. It encapsulates whether the call is permitted or blocked along with an optional reason for denial. This immutable value object facilitates clear decision-making before tool invocation.
